{"tid":1901737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民：反對畀錢差佬打香港人","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T03:57:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77dfdc3500b30cf9a54ebd7069ca27480f177cc5","tid":1901737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200228/4X44VQ23AHTPFFAT7NEWVDDOCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200228%2F4X44VQ23AHTPFFAT7NEWVDDOCU%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=51cd59f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200228%2F4X44VQ23AHTPFFAT7NEWVDDOCU%2F&h=26350fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200228/4X44VQ23AHTPFFAT7NEWVDDOCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民：反對畀錢差佬打香港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200228/large/1582821351_23e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200228%2Flarge%2F1582821351_23e3.jpg&h=e1e145b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【市民心聲】潘先生：「成個政府根本就係失敗，我寧願唔要一萬蚊都唔想佢哋（警隊）加撥款，加完之後都係打返香港人，情願佢哋啲錢畀中小企、低下階層仲好。」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】財政司司長陳茂波公佈的新一份財政預算案，焦點除了人人「回水」一萬元外，警隊大幅增加預算達258億元，升幅高達24%，更是為人詬病。本報走訪街頭，發現大部份市民對「回水」一萬元不感期待，但大力反對警隊增加預算，有市民諷刺地說：「你（警員）OT都O到買到樓啦！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拉布也無用 光復議會成出路<br />\n<br />\n促用款項買口罩予醫護<br />\n<br />\n何小姐打算將一萬元用來買清潔用品，但坦言派錢的作用不大，對於警隊增加巨額預算，她更感憤怒，認為在抗疫階段，醫護人員才是最需要幫助的部門，「我畀返一萬蚊你呀！唔好再加錢畀佢哋（警隊）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200228/large/1582821352_bb7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200228%2Flarge%2F1582821352_bb7d.jpg&h=71048a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【市民心聲】許先生：「我覺得唔係呢個時間去批錢畀佢哋（警隊），o依家個個都抗緊疫，你就撥款畀佢哋買裝甲車。o依家係應該買口罩畀醫護，畀好啲嘅設施佢哋。」<br />\n<br />\n潘先生認為政府應善用派錢款項為醫護採購口罩，現時仍增加警隊預算，是分化港人之舉，「都係加畀佢哋打返香港人，大家都明啦」，他反對綑綁式表決，寧願犧牲一萬元也不希望預算案通過。<br />\n<br />\n有基層市民亦認同派一萬元應與警察預算分拆表決，昨港台節目「財政司司長熱線」聽眾黃先生擔心，綑綁式表決會拖延派錢進度，「若政黨唔接受，一拖就唔知拖到幾時，呢一萬蚊對我哋好重要」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧珮瑤、陳詠恩"},{"pid":"5bb24d59bcd3103c2564ee71f7abcde904ebc230","tid":1901737,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"政府：哦"},{"pid":"0aca0524386fa636336e6e2b7b76205fdd06d0c2","tid":1901737,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾柒期牆紙】 工會抗暴政<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=4809dac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=8c7bd9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=4f2dcfff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffirsthand-news.web.app%2Fwallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=3db4a99c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aGdaRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%